				<a href="mailto:shic4@illinois.edu">shic4@illinois.edu</a>
				<span>/</span>
				<a href="https://github.com/Caesium135">GitHub</a>
				<span>/</span>
				<span>Champaign, IL</span>
			</div>
			<p class="bio">
				I am an undergraduate student interested in machine learning, scientific tools, and
				computational methods for experimental data. I currently work on nanoparticle analysis,
