			</p>
			<div class="experience-compact">
				<h2>Experience</h2>
				<div class="entry-list">
					<article class="entry-item">
						<div class="entry-heading">
							<h3>Murphy’s Group, University of Illinois</h3>
							<p>Feb 2026 – May 2026</p>
						</div>
						<p>
							Building a website tool for rod sizing with autonomous image processing and
							machine learning methods for noisy TEM/STEM images.
						</p>
					</article>

					<article class="entry-item">
						<div class="entry-heading">
							<h3>Murphy’s Group, University of Illinois</h3>
							<p>Feb 2025 – Feb 2026</p>
						</div>
						<p>
							Worked on nanoparticle synthesis, functionalization, characterization, and
							research data analysis.
						</p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section-block" id="news">
		<h2>News</h2>
		<p class="empty-state">No updates yet.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="section-block" id="posts">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>Posts</h2>
			<a href="/posts">All posts</a>
		</div>
		<p class="empty-state">No posts yet.</p>
